301
00:21:31,420 --> 00:21:32,950
S kým?

302
00:21:41,220 --> 00:21:45,190
<i> Tae Ik je váš záchranca, štylistka Jang!

303
00:21:45,530 --> 00:21:47,420
Môj záchranca?

304
