kvôli splateniu môjho dlhu.

375
00:26:14,300 --> 00:26:16,930
Ah! Naozaj?

376
00:26:16,940 --> 00:26:17,950
A čo ty, Lee Tae Ik?

377
00:26:17,950 --> 00:26:21,510
